---

# 1️⃣ defaults/main.yml (ALL VARIABLES)

👉 `roles/mstr_env/defaults/main.yml`

```yaml
# Namespace
namespace: mstr-env01

# Cluster domain (auto or override)
cluster_domain: ""

# Hostname
mstr_host: "{{ namespace }}.{{ cluster_domain }}"

# Istio ingress service
istio_ingress_service: istio-ingressgateway

# MSTR ingress service (from operator)
ingress_service: matr-env-istio-ingressgateway

# TLS Secret
tls_secret_name: mstr-tls-secret

# TLS cert paths (from VM)
tls_crt_path: /tmp/tls.crt
tls_key_path: /tmp/tls.key

# Route name
route_name: "route-{{ namespace }}"
```

---

# 2️⃣ Route Template (NO host)

👉 `templates/route.yaml.j2`

```yaml
apiVersion: route.openshift.io/v1
kind: Route

metadata:
  name: {{ route_name }}
  namespace: {{ namespace }}

spec:
  to:
    kind: Service
    name: {{ istio_ingress_service }}

  port:
    targetPort: https

  tls:
    termination: passthrough

  wildcardPolicy: None
```

✔ No `host`
✔ No `destinationCACertificate`
✔ Required for Istio

---

# 3️⃣ Istio Gateway Template (TLS TERMINATION)

👉 `templates/gateway.yaml.j2`

```yaml
apiVersion: networking.istio.io/v1beta1
kind: Gateway

metadata:
  name: {{ namespace }}-gateway
  namespace: {{ namespace }}

spec:
  selector:
    istio: ingressgateway

  servers:
  - port:
      number: 443
      name: https
      protocol: HTTPS

    tls:
      mode: SIMPLE
      credentialName: {{ tls_secret_name }}

    hosts:
    - "{{ mstr_host }}"
```

---

# 4️⃣ VirtualService Template

👉 `templates/virtualservice.yaml.j2`

```yaml
apiVersion: networking.istio.io/v1beta1
kind: VirtualService

metadata:
  name: {{ namespace }}-vs
  namespace: {{ namespace }}

spec:
  hosts:
  - "{{ mstr_host }}"

  gateways:
  - {{ namespace }}-gateway

  http:
  - match:
    - uri:
        prefix: /
    route:
    - destination:
        host: {{ ingress_service }}
        port:
          number: 80
```

---

# 5️⃣ TLS Task (CREATE CERT SECRET)

👉 `tasks/tls.yml`

```yaml
- name: Create TLS secret
  shell: >
    oc create secret tls {{ tls_secret_name }}
    --cert={{ tls_crt_path }}
    --key={{ tls_key_path }}
    -n {{ namespace }}
  ignore_errors: yes
```

---

# 6️⃣ Route Task

👉 `tasks/route.yml`

```yaml
- name: Render route YAML
  template:
    src: route.yaml.j2
    dest: /tmp/mstr-route.yaml

- name: Apply route
  command: oc apply -f /tmp/mstr-route.yaml
```

---

# 7️⃣ Istio Task

👉 `tasks/istio.yml`

```yaml
- name: Render Gateway
  template:
    src: gateway.yaml.j2
    dest: /tmp/mstr-gateway.yaml

- name: Apply Gateway
  command: oc apply -f /tmp/mstr-gateway.yaml

- name: Render VirtualService
  template:
    src: virtualservice.yaml.j2
    dest: /tmp/mstr-vs.yaml

- name: Apply VirtualService
  command: oc apply -f /tmp/mstr-vs.yaml
```

---

# 8️⃣ Main Task Flow

👉 `tasks/main.yml`

```yaml
# Get cluster domain dynamically
- name: Get cluster domain
  shell: oc get ingress.config.openshift.io cluster -o jsonpath='{.spec.domain}'
  register: cluster_domain_result

- set_fact:
    cluster_domain: "{{ cluster_domain_result.stdout }}"

# TLS
- import_tasks: tls.yml

# Route
- import_tasks: route.yml

# Istio
- import_tasks: istio.yml
```

